<tr><td nowrap width="20%" valign=baseline align=right><b>Notes: </b></td><td colspan=4 align=left valign=baseline>From the Owner's Manual: <i>Vacation America was designed to provide consumers with a reliable state of the art pinball machine for the home.</i><br><br>The places the player must visit are: New York, Philadelphia, Cape Canaveral, Everglades, Myrtle Beach, Washington D<ignore>C, Niagara Falls, Fort Knox, Detroit, Indianapolis, Atlanta, New Orleans, St. Louis, Chicago, Hot Springs, San Antonio, Roswell, Mount Rushmore, Yellowstone, Estes Park, Grand Canyon, Las Vegas, Yosemite, and Hollywood.<br><br>Harold Washington designed the processor and PC boards.<P></td></tr>
